ygData.subject: Re: twinked?
ygData.msgSnippet: Compared to a level 6 wizard with SMR.. No.. Oracle robe is doable on 30 with a group also and even staff of writhing.. Silversilk leggings are crappy common
ygData.messageBody:
Compared to a level 6 wizard with SMR.. No.. Oracle robe is doable on 30 with a group also and even staff of writhing.. Silversilk leggings are crappy common loot from magi(who drops SMR) and most people give them away to newbies or destroy them.. You have ok eq for level 30 but no where near twinked..

- Avron -
